   <div class="main_news_l fl"> 
    <h1>美媒：中国M99狙击步枪现身缅北 中国或军援佤邦(2/2)</h1> 
    <div class="detail"> 
     <em class="time">时间：2014-08-12 10:46:00</em> 
     <em class="form">来源：<a href="http://www.dianhen.com">军事网</a></em>
     <em class="form">热度:<script src="/e/public/ViewClick/?classid=6&amp;id=30377&amp;addclick=1"></script>℃</em> 
     <div class="font_sb"> 
      <span class="font"></span> 
      <div class="font_family"> 
       <em class="arrow_f"></em> 
